text: Carmen Eggens is a Canadian water polo player. She played for the Canadian women's national water polo team in the 2009 World Aquatics Championships, 2013 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2015 Pan American Games. She played for University of Hawaii's women's water polo team. == References == == Other websites == * Carmen Eggens competing for the Canadian Senior Women's water polo team montrealgazette.com Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian water polo players
